WEBVTT

00:00.047 --> 00:00.571
Okay, ready?

00:00.677 --> 00:01.199
Yes!

00:01.393 --> 00:01.718
Now!

00:03.349 --> 00:04.356
A Peloton?

00:04.505 --> 00:06.027
Give it up for our first time rider.

00:06.437 --> 00:07.017
First ride.

00:07.137 --> 00:08.535
I'm a little nervous but excited.

00:08.954 --> 00:09.475
Let's do this.

00:10.233 --> 00:11.222
5 days in a row.

00:11.511 --> 00:12.350
Are you surprised?

00:12.691 --> 00:13.172
I am.

00:13.835 --> 00:14.585
6 am.

00:14.735 --> 00:15.458
Yay.

00:15.562 --> 00:16.779
Rising with the sun.

00:17.029 --> 00:17.939
That was totally worth it.

00:18.097 --> 00:19.311
Let's go Grace in Boston!

00:20.161 --> 00:21.113
She just said my name.

00:21.613 --> 00:24.545
A year ago, I didn't realize how much this would change me.

00:26.289 --> 00:26.906
Thank you.

00:27.059 --> 00:29.727
This holiday, give the gift of Peloton.

